\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\Rightarrow9x=-11$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\Rightarrow x=-\dfrac{11}{9}$
\end_inset

 ( which lies in the interval defined by 
\begin_inset Formula $x<-\dfrac{9}{7}$
